  "informal_statement": "For every real x ≥ 2, ∫_2^x t⁻² dt = 1/2 − 1/x.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Direct antiderivative −1/t and the fundamental theorem of calculus on [2, x].",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem power_law_integral_two_to_x :\n    ∀ x : ℝ, 2 ≤ x → ∫ t in (2:ℝ)..x, ((t^2)⁻¹) = (2:ℝ)⁻¹ - x⁻¹",
